          Usertour
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-section background-color="#fff">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text font-size="20px"> Welcome to Usertour! </mj-text>
        <mj-text font-size="16px" color="#555" line-height="30px">
          <a href="{{url}}" target="_blank">Verify your email</a>
          to finish setting up your account.
        </mj-text>
